	<!-- Text  -->
	<!-- Notorious Pirate -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Notorious Pirate</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_HELP">
			<Text>A notorious pirate is known to spend his time ashore in one of our Harbor's taverns. His presence is attracting a slew of undiserables.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]So far, no one has been able to catch him.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Certainly no pirate I've ever heard of. Send some Navy official to deal with this, what's the worse that could happen?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>I've heard much of this sailor's exploits. Send an agent to present him with this letter of marque.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Though the local fishermen may not like it, I can see the benefits of having a legendary tavern.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>They say this man hordes his fortune in a rare type of Pearl. It would be unfortunate if someone were to... commandeer it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>{5_Turns} of [ICON_RESISTANCE] Rioting.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Spend 400 [ICON_GOLD] Gold to gain a Corvette.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>For {5_Turns} the Harbor gains +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and +4 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism, but nearby Fishing Boats lose -3 [ICON_FOOD] Food.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NOTORIOUS_PIRATE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Up to 2 Fishing Boats and the Harbor are destroyed. A [ICON_WAR] Barbarian Unit spawns. Gain a copy of the [ICON_RES_PEARLS] Pearls resource.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
